      "description": "\ud83d\ude99 Budget-Friendly & Ready to Go \u2014 A Practical Ride at an Honest Price! \u2014 Here's a straightforward opportunity for the savvy shopper! This car is in fair condition \u2014 it's mechanically functional and will get you where you need to go reliably day to day. There are some signs of wear consistent with its age, but nothing that gets in the way of everyday driving. If you're looking for dependable transportation without breaking the bank, this could be exactly what you need!",
