    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for the most budget-conscious way to get on the road? This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it has noticeable wear, cosmetic damage, and mechanical issues that will require attention. That said, it represents a real opportunity for a handy buyer or someone looking for a project car at a rock-bottom price. If you're mechanically inclined or just need something to work on, this could be your next diamond in the rough!",
