      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives, but has mechanical issues that will likely need attention before long. The exterior shows visible wear including scratches and minor dents. The interior has noticeable wear as well. Priced to sell as-is.",
      "price": 16500.0,
