    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and we are committed to complete transparency with every potential buyer. The exterior is truly exceptional \u2014 the paint finish is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like shine and absolutely no scratches, dents, or blemishes of any kind. Body panels are perfectly aligned, all trim pieces are intact and gleaming, and the glass is crystal clear throughout. The interior matches the exterior in every way: the upholstery shows zero wear, all surfaces are spotless, and every control, knob, and feature functions exactly as it did from the factory. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, with no leaks, no unusual noises, and strong, responsive performance. All mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, steering, transmission \u2014 operate smoothly and precisely. The tires have excellent tread depth remaining, and all electronics, including infotainment, climate control, and safety features, work perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for and presents as close to new as you will find on the used market.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in poor condition, and prospective buyers should carefully review this description before inquiring. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 there are multiple dents, scratches, and areas of paint fade or peeling that are clearly visible. The interior has seen better days, with worn and torn upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car has known issues that will require attention \u2014 it runs, but it is not reliable for daily use without repairs, and buyers should budget for meaningful mechanical work. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or seeking parts. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises, but no illusions either.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition, and we are proud to present one of the finest examples you'll find on the market. The exterior is essentially flawless \u2014 paint is deep, rich, and free of scratches, dents, or blemishes of any kind. Panel gaps are tight and uniform, and all trim pieces, lights, and glass are in perfect order. The interior is equally impressive: every surface is clean, unscuffed, and shows virtually no signs of use. Seats, carpets, headliner, and dashboard all look and feel as though they just left the showroom floor. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health \u2014 the engine runs smoothly and powerfully, all systems function exactly as intended, and there are no warning lights, unusual noises, or known issues of any kind. All electronics, climate control, infotainment, and safety features operate perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that truly needs nothing \u2014 no repairs, no cosmetic touch-ups, no surprises. Buy with complete confidence.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
